Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:39.52,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{奪われる為に生まれて来た人の群}And along with me, a bunch of others born just to get robbed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:42.80,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{きっとそうそうやって来る筈無い}And it won't be long before they come for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:44.95,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{救い無き砂上の僕は}I'm running helpless through the quicksand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:49.56,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{瘡蓋剥がし遊ぶ}Playing with scabs, trying to peel them off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:58.88,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{捨てられた偶像そこいらで見つけて}Here and there, neglected idols are all around me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:05.21,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{デタラメな色塗りたくって祈り捧ぐ}While painting them all with meaningless colors, I offer a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:09.61,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{真実は信じ続ける事にはじまる}The longer I go on believing in it, the more it becomes the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:15.20,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{粉々になって篩を抜ける時まで}Until it shatters to pieces small enough to escape the sieve
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:18.32,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{きっととうとうやって来たんかな}And I guess they've finally come for me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:20.30,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{答無き路上の僕も}Now I too walk the road without an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:24.03,Song,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{貴方の場所へ落ちる}At last, falling down to your place
Comment: 1,0:21:07.42,0:21:20.76,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}The heavy rain is over now, \NShadows have ceased to roam, \NEven summer itself has come to an end
Comment: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:20.76,Song,,0,0,5,,Ame wa yande ita kage to aruide ita natsu ga owatte ita
Comment: 1,0:21:20.76,0:21:34.34,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}My youth goes on, pushing me in my back with no rest,\NAnd the scarlet sky will soon start pouring water again
Comment: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:34.34,Song,,0,0,5,,Seishun ga boku no senaka o oshite akai sora utsuru mizutamari
Comment: 1,0:21:34.34,0:21:47.96,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}With my leg in a clutch, suddenly the sky shivered, \NSo unawares, making such stupid look!
Comment: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:47.96,Song,,0,0,5,,Ashimoto ga tora rete ite sora wa ureru bakaridatta
