Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.57,0:01:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Step by step, I get closer.{/It has finally come.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba, I'm heading for your spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to top off the evening...{/while we're at it/where were we}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?{/I'm listening}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ginya, what happened to Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking, \Nwhat the hell happened to Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't heard a thing \Never since you two split up?{unsure, it sounds like "when you are not together you haven't heard anything" but it may be something different, like "you haven't heard anything even though you two are together?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri did something out of line again{added}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't shown up yet. \NAnd it's well past her regular hour to start the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hour to start the work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she may have just overslept today.{/isn't it nothing more but oversleeping}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If that was the case, I wouldn't have minded. \NStill, usually, I'd be able to at least contact her somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can't get through, \Nnot even to her cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just overthinking it.\NAnyone is subject to oversleeping and absenteeism.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:03:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have thought so too, \Nhad our world been prevailed by the likes of you.{unsure, maybe "in our society, only the guys of your type think this way"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, if you learn something, \Ngive me a holler, deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So early, so redundant...{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Two new items.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Is this you, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying up late at night again? Gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, take your meal seriously!{/eat properly} I know you hate carrot, \Nbut it's not a reason to leave it on the plate{added}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you're getting sand for bones{/you'll get a fracture/your bones become fragile} \Nif you don't drink milk every morn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You always dine someplace else, don't you?{Lit eat outside/out, i.e. not at home}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Every once in a while, \N{it's better to }cook yourself, even if it's just rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You should at least be able to make boiled spinach \Nor some stir-fried vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lest you end up on a vitamin-short diet again.{/you tend to be deficient in vitamins} \NYou should realize{/grow concious of} it and be inventive{/devise a solution} on your own!{/yourself}{unsure, maybe "you should start doing this unconciously"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that's all,{/Well then,} \NI'll call you some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:04.41,Song,,0,0,0,,{unread/away from home}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,End of message.{/no more messages than that}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single time until now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I had this kind of feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I misappreciated{/undervalued} having her near me, \Nas{/thinking it was} just a natural order of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But now she's gone.{/nowhere to be found}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,towards{/about} Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so inattentive.{/without noticing}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Really been always feeling this way \Nwhile waiting for me?{unsure, maybe "has she really been waiting for me to understand her feelings/change this type of my feeling towards her"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She was to that extent anxious about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.28,Song,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya's stupid ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, you've completed your ascendance{/climb} \Nall the way up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya, you managed to put up a fight, \Nfar exceeding my estimations{/reckoning}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way \Nyou might have at least a chance to beat me.{Lit: had that not been so, you'd not defeat me}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is that another groundless worry?{/Lit: that too is unreasonable fear?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:08:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you won your way through to here \Nat a pace dwarfing my boldest estimation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm silent about it, \NI'll be in my prime condition, applying finishing touches{/bring it to the end in my ultimate/supreme condition}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite all...{/however}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be the one winning it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My determination{lit is ilness, but this sounds more coherent}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My determination will fend off{/avert/block/seal} the illness \Nfor the time being.{added}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give in{/lose}! \NNot until I fight Otonashi Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe, it's the first time we meet in person, \NOtonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let me congratulate you. \NThat was one fine match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Murasame Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner of Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- And how can I help the owner...\N- Today,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here for one special task.{/I've got something big to give to you}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.59,Song,,0,0,0,,To Mr. Otonashi Ginya
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... from Slothium?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been decided. The day for the score-settling{/ultimate/decisive} \Nshowdown{/battle} between you and Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Between me and Daiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a written evidence \Nof the Ultimate King challenging you.{/a letter of challenge from ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Put up a good fight! \NWith your everything on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you put up a half-assed{/clumsy} fight, \Ndon't expect me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to ever forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You were chosen for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,By the man wielding the Finger of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,By the Ultimate King,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,as the ultimate challenger.{/the last man to challenge him}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A {misty, lonely }chaser,{/lighter drink/water follow-up} huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad,{added} I have quit chasing{/the chase} already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to have a good night's sleep.{unsure, lit: once in a while, one needs a good sleep}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That exact line, \NI wish I could somehow propagate to him too.{unsure, just says "want to hear it exactly this way"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, a walking corpse{igai may be either this or except/unexpectedly none of which makes sense}, who put his life on the line - \Nonce he accomplishes this,{ afterwards}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what the hell is he waiting to happen?{this line is nigh pure guesswork - no clue who he refers to or this igai thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As well, as been longing for it with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:23.65,Song,,0,0,0,,To Mr. Otonashi Ginya
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{For }This one battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why though, to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium... No, pachislot in general \Nbrings people nothing but misfortunes{/sorrow/makes people unhappy}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of it, dad lost touch with us.{/had been separated/turned away from ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi seems to have gone cold too.{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, Yuri as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,really gained?{/profited}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I been pursuing{/looking/asking/wishing for}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first tried pachislot,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened to me?{guess, this may be "what happened to me since ..." or "what became of me" or "what was the first time I ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop! You shouldn't let that man in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am retiring from Slothium.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good bye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really have to lose everything I had?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't just deprive me of things{/steal from me/I didn't just lose}. \NAfter I got engrossed in pachislot{/Since meeting/coming across pachislot}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After I started fighting in Slothium, \NI gained something as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The chance to meet this motley crew of rivals{/I got to meet/came across many rivals}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Or this feeling of accomplishment, \Nuntranslatable into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba Ryo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,has been waiting.{unsure, maybe it's "I've been waiting" or "just you wait"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba is looking forward to fighting me!{/obsessed with the idea of fighting me/desires to fight me}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I too
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,must look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, my every thought \Nis directed towards fighting Daiba Ryo.{/my thoughs are only about ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With more passion than for anything else, \NI live for that fight only!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Unabated in looking forward, \Nwe{unspecified, maybe "I enter" or "We should enter"} enter the showdown for Slothium's #1.{/Lit: while continuing to yearn for it, Slotium's battle for the top/summit}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fight with my everything on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.90,Song,,0,0,0,,Nothing is as endless as the everlasting sky
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:48.00,Song,,0,0,0,,Nothing out there that is out of my reach
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:53.78,Song,,0,0,0,,Tonight's streetlights in between buildings sites\NAre too bright on me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:57.34,Song,,0,0,0,,For so long I \NDidn't know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:16:00.52,Song,,0,0,0,,What songs I sing \NAnd what songs I sang
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:06.22,Song,,0,0,0,,For long enough, the one offering love \NDoesn't want to know me now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:09.45,Song,,0,0,0,,But even if you get hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:12.59,Song,,0,0,0,,Even if it hurts a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:15.86,Song,,0,0,0,,In a little more, just a little more
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:18.87,Song,,0,0,0,,This pain will turn to joy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:25.04,Song,,0,0,0,,Say you hate me, say all you want\NYour words don't frighten me a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:30.98,Song,,0,0,0,,Cause if you do, your tomorrow, \NUnseen before, will die for good
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:37.38,Song,,0,0,0,,But how I loved you before, I love you now just as much
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.74,Song,,0,0,0,,\h\NHokkaido, Sapporo{there's some other character there too, I don't care} 20-264 \NKamoi Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It says Yuri returned to her hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't be back here any time soon{/in some while}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:46.52,Song,,0,0,0,,And how sincerely happy we were in old days\NI will never forget
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:58.94,Song,,0,0,0,,At any time, I want to keep in touch{何時でも 繋がっていたいし}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:02.01,Song,,0,0,0,,Even while asleep, I want to {always }watch over you{寝顔でも ずっと眺めてたいし}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:07.88,Song,,0,0,0,,Much more than that, \NI want to get to know you better{これ以上ない程あのひとを知りたいけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:11.16,Song,,0,0,0,,In all honesty, \Nthe more I give it a good ol' thought{本当にね 想えば想う程},
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:14.04,Song,,0,0,0,,The lyrics come out terribly off-spot{/unseemingly/unkempt}{詞はね見窄らしいものよ}{utaten says 詞, but I hear "uta" so I went for lyrics}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:20.16,Song,,0,0,0,,On Saturday, I walk down through the pouring rain,\NShivering and stooping{unsure what it means here, "to drop/to lose a match/to fall" - my guess is "hunching up because you were stood up again, shivering from rain"}, all alone{独りで土砂降りの土曜日震えて落とす}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:26.09,Song,,0,0,0,,But even the chill, \Neven this bitter chill{でも冷たさも この冷たさも}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:29.67,Song,,0,0,0,,In a little more, just a little more,{もう少し もう少し}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.85,Song,,0,0,0,,The stream will wash it all away{流すぐらいがいい}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:36.11,Song,,0,0,0,,Say you hate me, say all you want
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:39.11,Song,,0,0,0,,Your words don't frighten me a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:45.05,Song,,0,0,0,,Cause if you do, your tomorrow, \NUnseen before, will die for good
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:51.09,Song,,0,0,0,,But how I loved you before,\NI love you now just as much
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At last...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow{, then?/huh?}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep a wink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all your trouble.{I'm effectively guessing every word here, but this line is in my guts already so I give up, no point to write variants here as there's too many and I'm not sure in a single one}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You must win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As the one who always wins, Daiba Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibata from the engineering department. \NI know this is some unfortunate time to call.{/It must be very inconsiderate of me to call you at such an hour.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind.  \NHow is it looking?{/what about it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it. Conducting the last minute shakedown.\N{Aside from that, }Then a hotchpotch of other tests{added}, and we're ready in time{/somehow, we'll make it in time}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We're making it in time\Nfor a Daiba-Otonashi showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind it.{/don't say it}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to you that the machine we developed \Nfor a battle of the century will receive an explosive debut{/introduction}.{/that we can show off ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a dream come true.{/I would be forever satisfied/long-cherished ambition}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It may very well turn out \Nthe perfect{/most appropriate} machine for this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's completed, Yozakura Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The supreme{ form}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory.
